      <title>路透调查：预计中国将下调主要政策利率和贷款基准</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-expected-trim-main-policy-rate-lending-benchmarks-2024-09-19/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[路透社调查显示，美联储大幅降息消除了人民币大幅贬值的部分风险，市场普遍预计中国将于周五下调主要政策利率和基准贷款利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-expected-trim-main-policy-rate-lending-benchmarks-2024-09-19/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 06:04:25 GMT</pubDate>
