      <title>德意志银行将进一步削减分行网络</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/deutsche-bank-further-trim-branch-network-2024-09-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国德意志银行周三表示，该银行将进一步缩减其 400 家分支机构网络，从而关闭约 50 家较小的网点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/deutsche-bank-further-trim-branch-network-2024-09-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 16:21:02 GMT</pubDate>
